          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Corrections were done for",
                "- photon absorption, including the disk shape of the",
                "  samples and monitor foils, were calculated using",
                "  MCNP5 simulation of the detection geometry, have",
